<div class="background">

<div class="container pt-5">
  <div>
    <%= link_to "Add a new island", new_island_path, class: "btn btn-primary mt-3 btn-lg" %>
  </div>


  <div class="container pt-5">
   <h1>Welcome to Treasure Islands</h1>
    <p>Your treasure is our pleasure! Don't be like the rest and rent some stinky accommodation with bad karmic vibes.
      Spend some real money with us and rent out an entire island to yourself with zero nosy neighbors.
      As a great man once said, "Do what thou Wilt!".
      I mean, come on, if you have the money, why shouldn't you be able to do what you want, right?
      Sacrificial cats not supplied...</p>
  </div>

  <h2>Our Amazing Islands</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <% @islands.each do |island| %>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card">
          <%# <%= link_to image_tag("images/#{island.image_url}"), island_path(island) %>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title"><%= link_to island.name, island_path(island) %></h5>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
